CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 8, 1962, pg. 1 reads: "Grieved - Mrs. Emmett Woods is shown leaving Homestead's Second Baptist Church after funeral rites for her husband, one of Pittsburgh's young pioneers, whose death shocked the city. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Emmett Wood, being helped out of Second Baptist Church after Emmett Woods funeral, Homestead
